OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FIt's a chilling screenshot from UTV's
OL,8,Ffootage of a rally in Lurgan park in
OL,9,Ftribute to Natalie McNally.
OL,11,FDirectly behind the 32-year-old's
OL,12,Ffather Noel, as he unfurled a banner
OL,13,Ffor his daughter, walked the man who
OL,14,Fthis week was convicted of her brutal
OL,15,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FStephen McCullagh, a 36-year-old
OL,8,FYouTuber who also worked night shifts
OL,9,Fat the Belfast Telegraph, wore
OL,10,Ffeminist badges on his jacket and
OL,11,Fappeared to be holding the hand of
OL,12,Fanother woman.
OL,14,FBut he was keeping a low profile - to
OL,15,Fthe media anyway.
OL,17,FI was there too that weekend as our on
OL,18,Fduty reporter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FThe gathering was one of a number
OL,8,Facross Northern Ireland demanding
OL,9,Faction to both catch the person
OL,10,Fresponsible and to call out the
OL,11,Fscourge of violence against women and
OL,12,Fgirls.
OL,14,FPeople in the crowd we spoke to
OL,15,Frevealed their anger and sadness at
OL,16,Fwhat had happened to Natalie but also
OL,17,Ffear that the killer was still at
OL,18,Flarge.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FLittle did we know he was there, her
OL,8,Fpartner and father of her unborn
OL,9,Fchild, hiding in plain sight.
OL,11,FI interviewed Natalie's mum Bernie and
OL,12,Fbrother Brendan as well as a speaker
OL,13,Ffrom Women's Aid.
OL,15,FI then asked the family if Natalie's
OL,16,Fboyfriend would speak to us but he was
OL,17,Fnowhere to be found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FThe family protectively explained how
OL,8,Ftraumatised he had been by it all,
OL,9,Fgiven he had been the one who had
OL,10,Ffound her dead body.
OL,12,FTo me though he was conspicuous in his
OL,13,Fabsence.
OL,15,FI thought he would surely have been at
OL,16,Fthe family's side to support them and
OL,17,Fout of respect for his murdered
OL,18,Fgirlfriend.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FInstead, he lurked in the background
OL,8,Fwatching the tribute he had edited of
OL,9,FNatalie.
OL,11,FThe home videos of her as a toddler on
OL,12,Fholiday, in her first communion dress,
OL,13,Feven the ultrasound of the baby was
OL,14,Fbroadcast to the hundreds of people in
OL,15,Fthe crowd, moving many to tears.
OL,17,FGiven all that we know now, it sends
OL,18,Fshivers down my spine it's so sinister.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FStephen McCullagh was re-arrested and
OL,8,Fcharged just a few days later but it
OL,9,Fwas almost two months after the murder.
OL,11,FHe'd initially been ruled out as a
OL,12,Fsuspect because he said he'd been live
OL,13,Fstreaming on the night of the murder.
OL,15,FIt was an alibi which police had since
OL,16,Fdiscovered was fake.
OL,18,FThe stream had been recorded four days
OL,19,Fbefore as part of an elaborate cover
OL,20,Fup.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FMcCullagh thought he was some kind of
OL,8,Fcriminal mastermind but his web of
OL,9,Flies finally unravelled.
OL,11,FThe jury didn't buy his defence and
OL,12,Fjustice was served on Monday with an
OL,13,Funanimous guilty verdict.
OL,15,FNothing will bring Natalie back.
OL,17,FHer family are left with a legacy of
OL,18,Fpain and sorrow, grieving for a young
OL,19,Fwoman they adored and whose memory
OL,20,Fshould never be lost as we fixate on
OL,21,Fthe perpetrator.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774786269
OL,3,CKiller at large: Chilling footage
OL,4,Cshows murderer at Natalie McNally's
OL,5,Cvigil
OL,7,FThe judge has already told McCullagh
OL,8,Fhe faces a life sentence but the
OL,9,Ftariff is yet to be set.
OL,11,FGiven the aggravating factors - the
OL,12,Fpregnancy, the degree of premeditation
OL,13,Fand the lack of remorse - Natalie's
OL,14,Ffamily and society as a whole can only
OL,15,Fhope McCullagh faces an extremely long
OL,16,Ftime behind bars.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
